
Ranger Help for: myinfo
=======================

SYNTAX: myinfo
USAGE:  Any terrain.

SUMMARY:    
Myinfo shows a Ranger a number of important pieces of information about 
him or herself. It shows game information, such as level, guild level, 
experience and gold...but it also shows a Ranger information about his or
her standing as a Ranger, such as primary and secondary terrains, the
Ranger's current follower, and enemy species, as well as a list of skills
learned to that point.

=============================================================================
SEE ALSO: myskills, slots and learn

